</p></td>
   </tr>
   <tr>
    <td colspan="2"><p style="font-size: 13px; font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;">Please do not reply to this e-mail.</p>
      <p><b style="font-size: 13px; font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;">Orchard Supply Hardware</b><br>
        <span style="font-size: 12px; font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;">Phone: 1-888-SHOP-OSH (1-888-746-7674)</span><br>
        <span style="font-size: 13px; font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><a href="#">http://www.osh.com</a></span></p></td>
  </tr>
</table>
</div>
</body>
</html>
